plot(c(-1.5,1.5), c(-1.5,1.5), asp=1, type="n", ann=FALSE,
    axes=FALSE, xaxs="i", yaxs="i")
kcircle(col="#AA000088")
for (i in 1:6) kcircle(1,c(cos(i*pi/3),sin(i*pi/3)), col="#0000AA88")
